      "description": "Every time my aunt and uncle hosted one of their famous summer BBQs, these grilled Snickers pizza bites were on the menu. They’re quick, easy, and a crowd favorite. The kids would assemble them while the adults grilled the main course. After dinner, they’d pop them on the grill until golden brown, then dust with powdered sugar. Perfection!",
