      "aspect_ratio": "9:16",
      "description": "These crispy rice balls combine two amazing ingredients: kimchi and cheese! Not only are they easy to make, they also taste delicious and give you a satisfying crunch with a cheesy surprise inside.",
      "thumbnail_url": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/video-api-prod/assets/9adf7b1cb91d4f95a8f8148fcdf6aafc/reelsthumb.jpg",
