      "servings_noun_singular": "serving",
      "description": "Homemade ice cream in under 10 minutes? This 3-ingredient ice cream comes together with the help of a little ice and rock salt. It’s a great activity for kids to join in too. Top with your favorite toppings and enjoy all summer long!",
