          "position": 3,
          "display_text": "Assemble the toast: Spread ¼–⅓ cup of pea pesto over the toasted sourdough. Drape the prosciutto over the pesto and top with the poached egg. Finish with a drizzle of olive oil and a sprinkle of salt and pepper.",
